          "text" : "LLDB and WasmKit",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "For Swift ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "main",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " development snapshots, the toolchain includes enhanced support for debugging WebAssembly. The toolchain bundles ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "WasmKit",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : ", a runtime that can execute Wasm modules, and an LLDB with WebAssembly support.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "code" : "WasmKit",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " provides debugging capabilities through the GDB Remote Protocol. This allows you to use the version of LLDB bundled with the ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "main",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " snapshot toolchain to connect to a running ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "WasmKit",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " process for in-depth, command-line debugging.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "When using the ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "https:\/\/marketplace.visualstudio.com\/items?itemName=swiftlang.swift-vscode",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : " with a ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "main",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " snapshot toolchain, you can get a more integrated experience:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "inlineContent" : [
                        {
                          "text" : "Step through code:",
                          "type" : "text"
                        }
                      ],
